item.title: About
item.description: Hi, my name is seraphinush aka. seraph and i translate K TERA patch notes and more. aside from that i’m just your average TERA player with subpar DPS while playing my main Archer on Velika, NA TERA and Glory of Arun, K TERA. If you have any questions, my discord tag is seraphinush#5417, i’ll be happy to answer to the best of my knowledge.
